title: Moe's Southwest Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Southwestern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Nationwide franchise offering tacos, burritos, nachos, and rice bowls with vegan choices of black or pinto beans, organic tofu, rice, tortillas and veggies. Food is made to order in assembly line manner. Vegan items are not marked. Vegetarian items are marked with a V and can be made vegan by asking for no cheese and/or sour cream. No vegan cheese. Uses soybean oil and vegetable stock. No gelatin in guacamole. Fresh salsa bar.
